{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a7beeece66","title":"关于四川文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"859fcbf03f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"a7beeece66","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c42c8c4e2","type":"title","text":"关于四川文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a7beeece66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd8ddb6876","type":"paragraph","text":"从宜宾问题的揭发，才开始揭开了四川阶级斗争盖子的序幕，才开始揭开季井泉的盖子。四川文化大革命之所以困难，主要是刘、邓、李井泉搞的，他们把刘结挺打成反革命，把他们开除出党，这次才翻过来。以后要把这个材料印出来，发给每个党员。四川阶级斗争的揭盖子，两条路线斗争还未解决。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"a7beeece66","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":427,"end":427}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"088913a740","type":"title","text":"关于四川文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a7beeece66","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a7d9f610e","type":"paragraph","text":"从宜宾问题的揭发，才开始揭开了四川阶级斗争盖子的序幕，才开始揭开李井泉的盖子。四川文化大革命之所以困难，主要是刘、邓、李井泉搞的，他们把刘结挺打成反革命，把他们开除出党，这次才翻过来。以后要把这个材料印出来，发给每个党员。四川阶级斗争的揭盖子，两条路线斗争还未解决。（摘自林彪同志 1967 年 4 月 5 日关于四川问题的讲话）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"a7beeece66","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":576,"end":576}}}},"__N_SSG":true}